'''聖莫里茨奧林匹克滑冰場'''（{{lang-de|Eisstadion Badrutts Park}}）是一座位於[[瑞士|瑞士]][[聖莫里茨|聖莫里茨]]的室外體育場。它為[[冰球|冰球]]、[[競速滑冰|競速滑冰]]和[[花式滑冰|花式滑冰]]的比賽場地，也為[[1928年冬季奧林匹克運動會|1928年冬季奧林匹克運動會]]和[[1948年冬季奧林匹克運動會|1948年冬季奧林匹克運動會]]開閉幕典禮的舉辦場地。<ref>[http://www.aircanada.com/en/onair/february2010/eng-can-2/top5.html "Best Hosts of Olympic Winter Games Past"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606111804/http://www.aircanada.com/en/onair/february2010/eng-can-2/top5.html |date=2011-06-06 }}, ''onAir' magazine, Air Canada, February 2010</ref><ref>[http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1928/1928w2.pdf 1928 Winter Olympics official report.] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wXjHxjIZ?url=http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1928/1928w2.pdf |date=20110216152754 |dateformat=iso }} Part 2. pp. 1-7, 15. {{fr icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1948/ORW1948.pdf 1948 Winter Olympics official report.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1948/ORW1948.pdf |date=20080410085049 }} pp. 6, 21, 23. {{fr icon}} & {{de icon}}</ref>

